name: Fetch Youtube Channel Videos
author: Sohail Ahmed

sections.installation:
1. Install as regular WordPress plugin.

  2. Go your Pluings setting via WordPress Dashboard and activate it.

  3. After activating you will see a menu on left side and go to “Fetch Youtube Channel Videos” setting page and change your setting and save it.

  4. Enjoy!!!
sections.description:
“Now no need to update videos one by one, Just configure Plugin and add shortcode any where in website.”

Steps to Configure this plugin are mentioned in plugin admin panel. Just install and activate plugin, You will have all the details.
